arts.ttl: Colchester climb into League Two play-off places after five straight wins
arts.sum: Lyle Taylor, Owura Edwards and Jack Payne sealed a comfortable victory over Fleetwood.

arts.ttl: INTERVIEW: Rob Hunt happy to return to a winning Colchester United team
arts.sum: Hunt said: “It helps coming into a winning team when everyone’s confident and everyone’s got belief. “You’ve just got to stay mentally strong and keep working when you’re injured and try and wait for your opportunity and when you’re back fit, do your best when you get your opportunity.”
